<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1292260-what-is-the-significance-of-calum-wearing">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[What is the significance of Calum wearing a Celtic ring at the end of the novel? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
